{"tid":1412704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 - 成立民間獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:36:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T09:34:05.000Z","uid":285536,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4679471cddd3912479af71363f16ee5c66d9e52c","tid":1412704,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭宜家就係要拖，<br />\n我地要成立<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民間獨立調查委員會</span></span>，<br />\n民間自發搵的有代表性既人去做，<br />\n每日都<span style=\"color: red;\">叫埋記者市民去作供</span>，<br />\n唔好比林鄭每日開記者會洗腦。<br />\n<br />\n大家要記得<br />\n612 <br />\n71<br />\n721<br />\n728<br />\n83<br />\n84<br />\n政府既罪行<br />\n愈遲開始記憶就愈黎愈淺。<br />\n<br />\n民間獨立調查委員會並非大台，<br />\n功能只係負責調查，<br />\n完全唔代表示威者。<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊黎諗下！<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安。"},{"pid":"bd6fcc5ddfd2a3253e4c3a2b2f68a99a4bdf500d","tid":1412704,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9c9243a6044adee4e155d6b50faf0e5252d7637","tid":1412704,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n1"},{"pid":"bc52e9c205014d85e62e3c426fafce58d5a3c73c","tid":1412704,"uid":28604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:54:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"212386e1c0e67dcc213c09871f89a2de6dfdd7e5","tid":1412704,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26c9677116500f148b164e53f1df50bba9097551","tid":1412704,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"7f5346d43802be8bed8f2a9778b6d2598b24341c","tid":1412704,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"ec00e968c2cffb61a56f6d99da319fc103b73375","tid":1412704,"uid":285536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:13:16